          "date": "2013-01-18 10:57:47.000000000",
          "tz": 120
        },
        "subject": "LU-793 ptlrpc: Reconnections should not be refused...",
        "message": "LU-793 ptlrpc: Reconnections should not be refused...\n\nSince not letting clients with pending RPCs to reconnect caused a lot\nof problems, this patch allows such a reconnection and would only\nrefuse to process requests with the same xids that are already being\nprocessed. This patch is a port of LU-793 to b_neo_stable (2.2)\nRequests from Andreas were added also.\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-459\nReviewed-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <andriy_skulysh@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Iurii Golovach <iurii_golovach@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I9be309df0abd3f8b4c2078f7a5b46fad8865e5e7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
